---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-24">
      <img
        class="mx-auto h-auto w-full max-w-xl rounded-3xl object-cover"
        width="576"
        height="864"
        src="/assets/me.jpeg"
        alt="Abhinav Reddy Gotham"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        <!-- Mission description -->
        <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Our mission</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              At Trishakthi by ARG, our mission is to create spaces that resonate with your soul. 
              We believe that every home has a story to tell, and our role is to help you narrate it 
              through thoughtful design, aesthetics, and functionality.
            </p>
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              We strive to blend traditional Indian heritage with modern contemporary styles, 
              creating a unique fusion that stands the test of time. Our approach is holistic, 
              considering not just the visual appeal but the energy and flow of the space.
            </p>
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              Whether it's a cozy home or a bustling office, we bring the same level of passion, 
              precision, and dedication to every project. Your satisfaction and joy are our greatest rewards.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
